{"name":"cycle-http-server-driver","version":"0.0.1-alpha.4","description":"An HTTP server driver for CycleJS for managing request/response in Node.js.","main":"lib/src/http-server-driver.js","typings":"lib/src/http-server-driver.d.ts","files":["lib"],"scripts":{"prepublish":"typings install && npm run build","test":"node lib/test/http-server-driver.test","prebuild":"rimraf lib && mkdirp lib","build":"tsc","postbuild":"bin/remove-typings-ref lib/src/http-server-driver.d.ts","lint":"tslint -c tslint.json src/*.ts"},"license":"MIT","dependencies":{"@cycle/base":"^2.0.1","@reactivex/rxjs":"^5.0.0-beta.6"},"devDependencies":{"mkdirp":"^0.5.1","rimraf":"^2.5.2","tape":"^4.5.1","tslint":"^3.8.0","typescript":"^1.8.10","typings":"^0.8.1"},"peerDependencies":{"@cycle/core":"^7.0.0-rc4"},"repository":"https://github.com/mariuslundgard/cycle-http-server-driver","homepage":"https://github.com/mariuslundgard/cycle-http-server-driver#readme","gitHead":"585eeeb6a868c2a6106170ce48203b071f37c096","versions":[{"number":"0.0.1-alpha.4","date":"2016-04-26T20:49:47.206Z"}],"readme":"# cycle-http-server-driver\n\n*In alpha.*\n\nAn HTTP server driver for CycleJS for managing request/response in Node.js.\n\n## Installation\n\n```sh\nnpm install cycle-http-server-driver --save\n```\n\n## Documentation\n\n### Usage\n\n```js\nimport transport from 'http'\n\nimport {\n  makeHTTPServerDriver\n} from 'cycle-http-server-driver'\n\nimport bunyan from 'bunyan'\n\nconst port = 8080\nconst logger = bunyan.createLogger({name: 'web'})\nconst transport = makeHTTPServerTransport()\n\nconst drivers = {\n  HTTPServer: makeHTTPServerDriver(port, logger, transport)\n}\n\nfunction main (sources) {\n  return {\n    HTTPServer: sources.HTTPServer.map((context) => {\n      return {\n        ...context,\n        headers: {'Content-Type': 'text/html'},\n        body: 'Hello, world!'\n      }\n    })\n  }\n}\n\nrun(main, drivers)\n```\n","created":"2016-04-26T20:49:47.206Z","modified":"2016-04-26T20:49:47.206Z","l